36:26.000 --> 36:27.911
I was cleaning
the room next door,

36:27.920 --> 36:29.456
and I heard voices.

36:29.460 --> 36:31.496
Kinda loud--
that girl and a man,

36:31.500 --> 36:33.377
arguing, you know.

36:33.380 --> 36:35.280
And then she left
with him.

36:35.290 --> 36:38.077
Didn't seem thrilled
about going.

36:38.080 --> 36:39.206
What, um...

36:39.210 --> 36:40.108
What'd he look like?

36:40.120 --> 36:41.872
Uh, had on a uniform,

36:41.880 --> 36:44.280
like in the Army
or something.

36:44.290 --> 36:46.576
I could get in trouble
for saying it,

36:46.580 --> 36:48.662
you know,
so if anyone asks.

36:48.670 --> 36:51.070
Yeah. Yeah, uh...

36:51.080 --> 36:53.492
You know what,
hey, thank you.

36:55.080 --> 36:56.320
Hope your friend's okay.

36:58.960 --> 37:00.029
Thank you.

37:03.460 --> 37:05.246
[cartoon playing]

37:05.250 --> 37:08.572
[door opens]

37:08.580 --> 37:12.164
[ominous music]

37:15.080 --> 37:16.991
Chris, you're back.

37:19.540 --> 37:21.167
Yeah.

37:21.170 --> 37:23.206
I can't be out there.

37:23.210 --> 37:24.108
I can't do it.

37:25.120 --> 37:26.246
It's okay.

37:26.250 --> 37:28.036
I understand.

37:28.040 --> 37:30.076
We'll take
good care of you.

37:34.040 --> 37:35.996
Are you doing okay?

37:36.000 --> 37:37.035
Fine.

37:37.040 --> 37:39.417
To see you
transform like that,

37:40.830 --> 37:42.240
it was magnificent.

37:43.250 --> 37:44.319
[door opens]

37:46.750 --> 37:48.206
[Leena]
How are you doing?

37:48.210 --> 37:49.199
Everything okay?

37:49.210 --> 37:51.826
Yes. I am ready for baby.

37:53.620 --> 37:55.030
What is that?

37:55.040 --> 37:57.031
That's just
a mild tranquilizer.

37:57.040 --> 37:58.325
Help her relax,

37:58.330 --> 38:00.161
stay still
for the implantation.

38:05.750 --> 38:07.741
It'll take a moment
or two to work.

38:07.750 --> 38:09.240
I'll be back.

38:11.080 --> 38:12.616
[door opens]

38:12.620 --> 38:13.666
[door closes]

38:22.250 --> 38:24.115
[ominous music]

38:24.120 --> 38:25.326
You'll feel drowsy
for a little while.

38:25.330 --> 38:27.036
Try to stay
as still as possible.

38:30.080 --> 38:32.116
The procedure
went exceptionally well.

38:34.290 --> 38:35.450
And Ryn?

38:35.460 --> 38:36.666
Not yet.

38:36.670 --> 38:38.877
I implanted
the first embryo in you.

38:38.880 --> 38:40.825
She'll receive the second.

38:40.830 --> 38:42.707
Okay.

38:42.710 --> 38:43.995
I'll pray for us both.

38:49.750 --> 38:50.819
[door closes]

38:57.500 --> 38:59.070
What are you doing here?

39:00.120 --> 39:01.951
This is a female ritual.

39:01.960 --> 39:03.109
And you include him?

39:03.120 --> 39:04.576
[Beth]
We needed his help.

39:04.580 --> 39:05.990
How did you know
about this?

39:08.210 --> 39:10.610
-I'm in charge here.
-Are you?

39:12.170 --> 39:14.661
This is supposed to be
a safe place for us,

39:14.670 --> 39:17.571
and you welcome him here,
a Pownall.

39:17.580 --> 39:20.378
She's choosing the family
that killed our people.

39:20.380 --> 39:21.824
We can't keep living
in the past,

39:21.830 --> 39:23.570
worrying about threats
that don't exist.

39:23.580 --> 39:24.990
It happened once.

39:25.000 --> 39:26.536
It'll happen again.

39:26.540 --> 39:28.326
Nothing good comes
from that family.

39:28.330 --> 39:30.378
That's not true.

39:30.380 --> 39:33.201
I've sacrificed
everything for us,

39:33.210 --> 39:34.575
to protect us.

39:36.620 --> 39:37.700
And I'm one of them.

39:39.040 --> 39:40.109
What do you mean?

39:40.120 --> 39:41.610
I am a Pownall.

39:41.620 --> 39:42.826
And so am I.

39:44.080 --> 39:46.992
[ominous music]

40:10.120 --> 40:12.076
How long have you
known this for?

40:12.080 --> 40:14.287
I only told her
the last time I was here.

40:14.290 --> 40:16.702
She's kept you safe
all these years.

40:16.710 --> 40:18.075
She deserves your trust.

40:18.080 --> 40:19.160
Not anymore.

40:19.170 --> 40:20.706
I'm going.

40:20.710 --> 40:22.746
Who's with me?

40:31.920 --> 40:32.989
[Bryan]
You'll regret this.

40:35.960 --> 40:36.949
[door opens]

40:39.460 --> 40:41.166
-[door closes]
-[Leena] Ryn!

40:45.210 --> 40:47.701
-She's gone!
-Come on!

40:47.710 --> 40:50.110
[female singer]
'Cause everybody talks

40:50.120 --> 40:51.417
[Ben] No! No!

40:51.420 --> 40:53.786
- Tell me your sin
-Ryn!

40:53.790 --> 40:55.109
Ryn!

40:55.120 --> 40:57.782
Nobody forgives

40:57.790 --> 41:00.372
Hey! Ian! Ian, stop!

41:00.380 --> 41:02.826
-Stop! Hey! Hey!
-[Maddie] Ryn!

41:04.420 --> 41:08.379
'Cause everyone is scared

41:08.380 --> 41:12.111
But nobody cries

41:12.120 --> 41:14.372
Nobody dares

41:14.380 --> 41:18.828
Speak to you

41:18.830 --> 41:21.071
[Warren] Ian, a call
this late better be good.

41:21.080 --> 41:22.206
You wanted evidence, right?

41:23.250 --> 41:24.490
I got it.

41:31.120 --> 41:34.203
[dramatic music]

41:36.580 --> 41:39.993
[music playing]
